Package jspecview.common

Interface Summary
Graph Interface Graph provides methods that are used for the display by the JSVPanel.
 

Class Summary
Coordinate The Coordinate class stores the x and y values of a coordinate.
IntegralGraph class IntegralGraph implements the Graph interface.
IntegrateDialog Dialog for inputing values for the calulation of the IntegralGraph.
JDXSpectrum JDXSpectrum implements the Interface Spectrum for the display of JDX Files.
JSpecViewFileFilter A implementation of the FileFilter that filters out all files except those with extensions that are added.
JSpecViewUtils JSpecViewUtils contains static methods used to calculate values for display of spectra and other utility methods used in the application.
JSpecViewUtils.MultiScaleData The inner class of JSpecViewUtils that stores information about scale and range that JSVPanel needs to to display a graph with a mutliple plots.
JSpecViewUtils.ScaleData The inner class of JSpecViewUtils that stores information about scale and range that JSVPanel needs to to display a graph with a single plot.
JSVPanel JSVPanel class draws a plot from the data contained a instance of a Graph.
JSVPanelPopupListener JSVPanelPopupListener shows the popup menu on JSVPanels when the right mouse button is clicked.
JSVPanelPopupMenu Popup Menu for JSVPanel.
OverlayLegendDialog Dialog for showing the legend or key for overlayed plots in a JSVPanel.
PrintLayoutDialog Dialog to set print preferences for JSpecview.
TransmittanceAbsorbanceConverter class TransmittanceAbsorbanceConverter converts a JDXSpectrum from Transmittance to Absorbance and vice versa.
Visible Visible class - for prediction of colour from visible spectrum
